org.mpxj.mspdi

Class DatatypeConverter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mpxj.mspdi.DatatypeConverter

  • public final class DatatypeConverter
extends Object
    This class contains methods used to perform the datatype conversions required to read and write MSPDI files.
